List entries from the citation-backed decision log

Usage: mxr decisions [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --topic <TOPIC>
      --since <SINCE_DAYS>
      --limit <LIMIT>       [default: 50]
      --format <FORMAT>     [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help                Print help
